title: BSkyB Star Wars The Force Awakens 2of2 Sky Movies Preview Specia

Star Wars: The Force Awakens

Arts Documentary hosted by Alex Zane, published by BSkyB in 2015 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/d/de/Star-Wars-The-Force-Awakens-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Star Wars: The Force Awakens
We've had the glitzy Hollywood shindig but now it's time for the UK premiere of Star Wars: The Force Awakens


1)  Premiere Live 
Alex Zane hits the red carpet to chat to the cast and crew of Star Wars: The Force Awakens.

2)  Preview Special 
Sky Movies takes a special look at the newest instalment in the epic intergalactic saga....
